title: Grateful Dead Live at Studio on 1971-09-28
lineage: Cassette source transfers (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 > Samplitude Pro X5 > Flac2496
description:
Set I
(A) Playing, Jack Straw, Deep Elm, Big RxR Blues, Promised, Attics (9/30/71)
Set II
(B) Bird Song, Jack Straw, Mama Tried, Uncle John's Jam, Me & My Uncle(9/29/71)
Mexicali (9/30/71)
Set III
Candyman, Cumberland, El Paso, Jam, Cold Rain (9/28/71)
Comment
Keith's Rehearsals Sessions 9/28 thru 10/1/71
